data.description: Upon entering this beautiful architecturally interesting, updated home, you are greeted with open concept floor plan.  You will see the gran piano and vaulted ceilings, which is only the beginning. The kitchen has been renovated with new stainless appliances, wood cabinetry, quartz counters and tile backsplash.  Master bedroom is a grand size with newly renovated master bath and fitted closet.  There are dual sinks, new frameless shower door and new lighting fixtures.  Third bedroom/den has glass doors, designer fixture and new plank flooring.  The guest bath as been remodeled with granite counters and tub with updated designer touches.  There is a great room prefect for entertaining your guests.  All closets have been updated and fitted. The private backyard is perfect for relaxing and enjoying your company.  There is also a screen patio for your outdoor enjoyment.  Don't miss this opportunity to own this updated home in Addison Green.
